<%- include('partials/header', {
  title: 'Booking Policies & FAQ | J&M Serenity Spa',
  description: 'Booking policies, cancellation policy, and frequently asked questions for J&M Serenity Spa in Highlands Ranch, CO.',
  activePage: 'policies'
}) %>

<main>
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="eyebrow reveal">Policies &amp; FAQ</p>
      <h1 class="reveal">Booking Policies</h1>
      <p class="lead muted reveal" style="max-width: 68ch;">
        Everything you need to know before your visit.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container content" style="max-width: 720px;">

      <div class="card reveal" style="padding: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
        <h2>Appointment Policy</h2>
        <p>All sessions are by appointment only. Walk-ins are welcome based on availability, but we recommend booking in advance to secure your preferred therapist and time.</p>
        <p>Please arrive 5–10 minutes before your scheduled appointment to settle in and complete any intake forms if it's your first visit.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="card reveal" style="padding: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
        <h2>Cancellation &amp; Rescheduling</h2>
        <p>We understand plans change. We ask that you provide at least <strong>24 hours' notice</strong> if you need to cancel or reschedule your appointment.</p>
        <p>Late cancellations or no-shows may be subject to a cancellation fee. Repeated no-shows may require a deposit to hold future appointments.</p>
        <p>You can manage your appointment using the link sent to you via text or email at the time of booking.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="card reveal" style="padding: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
        <h2>Payment</h2>
        <p>Payment is collected at the time of your appointment. <strong>We do not collect payment online.</strong></p>
        <p>We accept cash, credit cards, debit cards, Zelle, Venmo, and gift certificates.</p>
        <p>Tips are appreciated and can be added at checkout.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="card reveal" style="padding: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
        <h2>Gift Certificates</h2>
        <p>Gift certificates are available for any dollar amount and make a wonderful gift. They can be purchased in person or by phone.</p>
        <p>Each certificate has a unique code that is verified at checkout — simply present your code at your appointment. Gift certificates are non-refundable and have no expiration date.</p>
        <p><a href="/gift-certificates">Check your gift certificate balance</a></p>
      </div>

      <div class="card reveal" style="padding: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
        <h2>Late Arrivals</h2>
        <p>If you arrive late, your session may be shortened to avoid impacting the next client's appointment. The full session rate will still apply.</p>
        <p>If you are more than 15 minutes late without contacting us, your appointment may be considered a no-show.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="card reveal" style="padding: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
        <h2>Health &amp; Safety</h2>
        <p>Please let your therapist know about any health conditions, injuries, allergies, or areas of concern before your session begins.</p>
        <p>If you are feeling unwell, have a fever, or have a contagious condition, we ask that you reschedule your appointment for your safety and the safety of our staff and other clients.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="card reveal" style="padding: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
        <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

        <p><strong>What should I wear?</strong><br />
        Wear whatever is comfortable. You will be properly draped during your session at all times. Undress to your comfort level.</p>

        <p style="margin-top: 1rem;"><strong>Can I request a specific therapist?</strong><br />
        Absolutely. You can choose your preferred therapist during the booking process, including specifying a gender preference.</p>

        <p style="margin-top: 1rem;"><strong>What if I need to cancel last minute?</strong><br />
        We understand emergencies happen. Please call or text us as soon as possible. We do our best to accommodate, but a cancellation fee may apply for same-day cancellations.</p>

        <p style="margin-top: 1rem;"><strong>Do you offer couples massages?</strong><br />
        Yes! We have dedicated couples rooms. Select a couples service when booking and both guests will be in the same room.</p>

        <p style="margin-top: 1rem;"><strong>Is there parking?</strong><br />
        Yes, free parking is available at our location.</p>

        <p style="margin-top: 1rem;"><strong>How do I redeem a gift certificate?</strong><br />
        Simply provide your gift certificate code when you check in for your appointment. The amount will be applied to your session.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="cta-row reveal">
        <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/book">Book Now</a>
        <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="/contact">Still Have Questions?</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>
